Title: The Extreme Magic Of Eric Wilzig
Description: As host Nick Cannon stated during Eric's recent appearance on NBC's hit TV show America's Got Talent, "Wow, Eric, that was amazing! How did you do that?" Combining big stage illusions, daring stunts, heart-racing escapes, special effects, cool music and more, "The Extreme Magic of Eric" guarantees a show that  Rutgers Day attendees will never forget!  www.ExtremeMagicOfEric.com
